graph LR
    Dashboard["odh-dashboard<br/>Web Console"]

    %% Deployment Dependency
    Dashboard -.->|deployed by| Operator["RHOAI Operator<br/>(kustomize manifests)"]

    %% Authentication Dependency
    Dashboard -->|auth sidecar| KRBP["kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(odh-kube-auth-proxy)"]

    %% Core Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|all resource CRUD| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|ingress routing| GatewayAPI["Gateway API<br/>(data-science-gateway)"]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (CRD Watch)
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: Notebook| NotebookCtrl["Kubeflow Notebook<br/>Controller"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: InferenceService| KServe["KServe"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: DataScienceCluster| DSC["DataScienceCluster"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: DSCInitialization| DSCI["DSCInitialization"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: ModelRegistry| ModelReg["Model Registry"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: MLflow| MLflowOp["MLflow Operator"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: FeatureStore| FeastOp["Feast Operator"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: LlamaStackDistribution| LlamaStack["Llama Stack"]
    Dashboard -->|CRD watch: GuardrailsOrchestrator| TrustyAI["TrustyAI"]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (REST API proxy)
    Dashboard -->|REST proxy /api/service/pipelines| DSP["Data Science<br/>Pipelines<br/>8443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|REST proxy /api/service/mlmd| MLMD["ML Metadata<br/>8443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|REST proxy /api/service/modelregistry| ModelRegAPI["Model Registry<br/>API 443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|REST proxy /api/service/trustyai| TrustyAIAPI["TrustyAI<br/>443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|REST proxy /api/service/model-serving| ModelServAPI["Model Serving<br/>API 443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|PromQL queries| Thanos["Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9092/TCP"]

    %% BFF Module Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|Gen AI BFF| LlamaStackAPI["Llama Stack<br/>Inference 443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|Gen AI BFF| MCPServers["MCP Servers"]
    Dashboard -->|MaaS BFF| MaaSBackend["MaaS Backend"]
    Dashboard -->|MLflow BFF| MLflowTracking["MLflow Tracking<br/>Server"]
    Dashboard -->|AutoML/AutoRAG BFF| S3["S3-compatible<br/>Storage 443/TCP"]
    Dashboard -->|AutoML BFF| KFPipelines["Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>(via DSPA)"]

    %% External Integrations
    Dashboard -->|CRD + Secret| NIM["NVIDIA NIM"]
    Dashboard -.->|ConsoleLink CR| Console["OpenShift Console"]
    Dashboard -.->|optional telemetry| Segment["Segment Analytics"]
    Dashboard -.->|observability| Perses["Perses<br/>8080/TCP"]

    %% Consumers (who integrates with dashboard)
    Users["Data Scientists /<br/>ML Engineers"] -->|web UI| Dashboard

